ActControlled Drugs and Substances Act
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULES I AND III to the CONTROLLED DRUGS AND SUBSTANCES ACT (METHAMPHETAMINE) by adding this substance to Schedule I and amending its present listing on Schedule III, thereby increasing the severity of the penalties associated with offences involving this substance.
